00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
This could be the most important minute of your day.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:11,000
We have been through difficult times and faced big problems ahead.

3
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:17,000
But every crisis contains both danger and opportunity.

4
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:19,000
You can play your part.

5
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:21,000
Right now.

6
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Please close your eyes.

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:27,000
Imagine the better future we could have.

8
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:31,000
Imagine that future.

9
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:34,000
What does it look like for you?

10
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:35,000
For the people you love.

11
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:37,000
How do we lift each other up?

12
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:39,000
And make it fair.

13
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:40,000
How do we protect nature?

14
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:43,000
And save our sad homes?

15
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:49,000
Picture that future you want.

16
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:53,000
Now open your eyes.

17
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:58,000
It's time to talk about the future we want.

